metrized product states and we always\nprovide explicit rates of convergence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Sep 2014 17:08:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Jan 2016 13:24:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-29"}
