 SC slots.We estimate that around 400 such\ntargets are now available for study in the Kepler LC archive. That number could\npotentially be a lot higher for K2, since there will be a new target list for\neach of its campaigns.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Sep 2014 13:10:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Sep 2014 12:23:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
